ely place 5 charges on all the rogue masks.  Probably shut the everquest site down with all the hate mail.<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Levitation can no longer be used in The Deep. </i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>/waves bye bye to yet another zone where DMF would be useful. <br><br><br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  A player character will always have a name over its head, even if they are skeleton. </i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->  <br>A minor nerf, but a still a nerf.<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Dire Charm should no longer break (this was actually patched earlier along with an emergency patch. </i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Well great you fixed a bug that you didn't get right first time. <br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Necromancer Group spells should now be working, they were only affecting the caster. This includes spells such as: Degeneration, Succession of Shadows, Crippling Claudication, and Zavfeer's Theft of Vitae. These spells have also had their duration increased. Mind Wrack will be fixed soon. </i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>I kinda liked getting all the buffs myself, but I guess the group will be a little happier now.  It was a given if verant had to take time to fix the spells they didn't get right first time, we were going to pay something for the inconvenience. <br><br><br><br><br> <p><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~mbielak/_uimages/Posiden.gif></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/bnamelesstavern.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=posiden>Posiden</A> at: 1/8/02 10:29:38 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/bnamelesstavern.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=posiden>Posiden</A></s